# Python maintainer tools

## Pipelines

- **`tools/data_refresh/`** — wiki/Steam fetch, parse, merge, optional LLM tag proposals. See **`tools/data_refresh/README.md`**. Never commit **`config.yaml`** (use **`config.example.yaml`** + env vars).
- **`tools/run_insights/`** — aggregate telemetry from **`events.jsonl`** or export ZIPs; does not rewrite production JSON.

## Style

- **Ruff** is the formatter/linter (`pyproject.toml`). Run **`ruff format .`** before finishing.
- **`tools/data_refresh/main.py`** intentionally adjusts **`sys.path`** before imports (E402/I001 ignored in Ruff config).
- Use **`PYTHONPATH=.`** from repo root when running **`python -m tools.run_insights`**.

## LLM in tooling

- **`heuristics-analyze`** may call Chat Completions when **`api_key_env`** is set even if runtime **`llm.enabled`** is false.
- Tag proposals must stay within **`SUPPORTED_TAGS.md`** vocabulary.
